App Support
Thank you for using our app! We're here to help if you encounter any issues or have questions.
How to Get Support

Check the FAQ: Many common questions are answered in our FAQ section.
Search Existing Issues: Before creating a new support ticket, please search our GitHub Issues to see if your question has already been addressed.
Create a New Issue: If you can't find a solution, please create a new issue on our GitHub repository.
Emergency Support: For urgent issues affecting your business operations, please email us at support@yourapp.com.

What to Include in Your Support Request
To help us assist you more effectively, please include:

A clear description of the issue
Steps to reproduce the problem
Your app version
Your operating system and version
Any relevant screenshots or error messages

Support Hours
Our team monitors support requests Monday through Friday, 9 AM to 5 PM EST. We strive to respond to all inquiries within 24 business hours.
Feature Requests
We love hearing your ideas! Please submit feature requests through our GitHub Discussions page.
Thank you for your patience and for helping us improve our app!
